OL,3,CWork to begin on new #1.25bn electric
OL,4,Carc furnace in Port Talbot
OL,6,FTata Steel will mark the start of its
OL,7,Fmove towards greener steel production
OL,8,Fat Port Talbot's steelworks on Monday.
OL,10,FThe steel giant is progressing with
OL,11,Fits construction of a #1.25bn electric
OL,12,Farc furnace (EAF) in the town, which
OL,13,Fis set to be up and running by the end
OL,14,Fof 2027.
OL,16,FGovernment ministers will join Tata
OL,17,Fbosses at a groundbreaking event at
OL,18,Fthe Port Talbot site later today
OL,19,F(Monday 14th July) to mark the
OL,20,Fbeginning of the furnace's
OL,21,Fconstruction.
