OL,6,FNatarajan Chandrasekaran, chairman of
OL,7,FTata Steel and the Tata Group,
OL,8,Fdescribed the moment as an "important
OL,9,Fday for Tata Group, Tata Steel and for
OL,10,Fthe UK".
OL,12,FHe added: "At Port Talbot, we are
OL,13,Fbuilding the foundations of a cleaner,
OL,14,Fgreener future, supporting jobs,
OL,15,Fdriving innovation and demonstrating
OL,16,Four commitment to responsible industry
OL,17,Fleadership."
