OL,3,CWork to begin on new #1.25bn electric
OL,4,Carc furnace in Port Talbot
OL,6,FThe electric arc furnace (EAF) will be
OL,7,Fbuilt on the site of the Port Talbot
OL,8,Fsteelworks, in the area of the
OL,9,Fexisting Basic Oxygen Steelmaking
OL,10,F(BOS) plant.
OL,12,FIt is thought that it will be one of
OL,13,Fthe largest furnaces of its kind in
OL,14,Fthe world, melting mostly scrap steel
OL,15,Fto produce 3 million tonnes of steel
OL,16,Fper year.
OL,18,FTata insists the move will cut Port
OL,19,FTalbot's emissions by 90%, while
OL,20,Fensuring the future of steel
OL,21,Fproduction in the town.
