OL,3,CWork to begin on new #1.25bn electric
OL,4,Carc furnace in Port Talbot
OL,6,FIt comes after Tata Steel closed the
OL,7,Fplant's last blast furnace in
OL,8,FSeptember last year.
OL,10,FThe move put over 2,800 jobs at risk
OL,11,Fand brought traditional steel-making
OL,12,Fto an end in the town.
OL,14,FAround 2,500 workers are thought to
OL,15,Fhave left the business by March 2025,
OL,16,Fwith many having already left by the
OL,17,Fend of last year.JA further 300 roles
OL,18,Fare set to be affected in the next
OL,19,Fthree years.
