OL,3,CWork to begin on new #1.25bn electric
OL,4,Carc furnace in Port Talbot
OL,6,FThe UK Government has backed plans for
OL,7,Fthe EAF with a #500 million
OL,8,Finvestment, saying that 5,000 UK jobs
OL,9,Fhave been secured as a result of its
OL,10,Fconstruction.
OL,12,FAhead of the groundbreaking event,
OL,13,FCommunity Assistant General Secretary
OL,14,FAlasdair McDiarmid said: "This
OL,15,Fbittersweet day is a consequence of
OL,16,Fthe devastating closure of the blast
OL,17,Ffurnaces, but importantly a future for
OL,18,FPort Talbot steelmaking is being
OL,19,Fsecured.
