OL,6,FThe survey found that 74% of
OL,7,Fhouseholds are expecting to experience
OL,8,Fsome form of financial pressure in the
OL,9,Fnext six months, specifically with
OL,10,Fenergy bills (56%), food (44%) and
OL,11,Fhousing (26%).
OL,13,FNeath Port Talbot Council Leader Cllr
OL,14,FSteve Hunt said the Tata Steel / Port
OL,15,FTalbot Transition Board was
OL,16,Festablished in response to the job
OL,17,Flosses, which has been providing #100
OL,18,Fmillion of funding to support workers,
OL,19,Fbusinesses, and affected communities.
