OL,10,Fin the area, an industry which has
OL,11,Fprovided quality jobs to local people
OL,12,Ffor generations.
OL,14,F"The start of the construction phase
OL,15,Fis good news for Port Talbot and
OL,16,Fneighbouring communities, and I'm
OL,17,Fespecially pleased that Tata has
OL,18,Fcommitted to employing local
OL,19,Fcontractors and local workers where it
OL,20,Fcan."
